restrictions on the use of codes by category. If a code is
appropriate for an observed malfunction, it may be used regardless
of what category it is listed. Avionics shops may use engine
codes. Engine shops may use avionics codes. Tire shops may use
physical/mechanical, avionic or engine codes, etc. Categories of
